<div class="container mb-5">
  <%= render "shared/tutorial" %>
  <div class="container about-container">
    <!-- Header Section -->
    <header class="about-header">
      <h1 class="animate-header">About Needpedia</h1>
      <div class="header-accent animate-accent"></div>
    </header>

    <!-- Founder Section -->
    <section class="profile-section alternating-section">
      <div class="profile-content animate-slide-left">
        <div class="profile-image">
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <%= image_tag 'Anthony_Brasher.png', alt: 'Anthony Brasher', class: 'profile-img' %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="profile-text">
          <h2>Meet Our Founder<br><span class="highlight">Anthony Brasher</span></h2>
          <blockquote>
            "I've been an activist my entire life, and started working on Needpedia around the time of the Occupy
            Movement. That experience made me realize that it is actually primitive and barbaric that there's no
            official archive for solutions to problems facing humanity.
            We can keep track of every legal mistake billions of people make in their entire lives, in perpetuity,
            without question, but if you want to see what ideas people have for solving problems that literally kill
            hundreds of thousands of people every year, nothing! I really think people are going to look back on that in
            awe."
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Lead Engineer Section -->
    <section class="profile-section alternating-section reverse">
      <div class="profile-content animate-slide-right">
        <div class="profile-image">
          <div class="image-wrapper">
            <%= image_tag 'Murtaza.png', alt: 'Murtaza Zarkhwan', class: 'profile-img' %>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="profile-text">
          <h2>Lead Engineer<br><span class="highlight">Murtaza Zarkhwan</span></h2>
          <blockquote>
            "I live in a remote area in Pakistan far away from cities where I enjoy the peace and quiet and can focus on
            my work. I prefer having few people around me who are pure rather than a crowd where nobody cares.
            I am a problem solver and help people solve their problems using my skills in web development. I had a hard
            background, so I now work to make sure others don't have to. I've seen too much from a very young age, I
            have survived terrorism, wars, floods, and earthquakes. That's why I appreciate every day of my life."
          </blockquote>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Mission Section -->
    <section class="mission-section">
      <div class="mission-content animate-scale">
        <div class="mission-visual">
          <div class="logo-container">
            <%= image_tag 'Needpedia_logo.png', alt: 'Needpedia Logo', class: 'mission-img' %>
          </div>
          <div class="visual-accent"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-text">
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p class="lead">Creating the world's premier solution archive for humanity's greatest challenges</p>
          <p>The world is facing extremely serious problems, and yet there's still no archive for solutions to them. We at Needpedia seek to create the finest place on Earth for citizens and experts to share ideas and collaborate.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- AI Section -->
    <section class="ai-section">
      <div class="ai-intro animate-fade-in">
        <h2>Our Digital Librarians</h2>
        <p class="subheading">AI systems named after heroic librarians who resisted oppression</p>
      </div>

      <div class="ai-grid">
        <article class="ai-card animate-card">
          <div class="ai-image">
            <%= image_tag 'Lotte_Bergtel-Schleif.png', alt: 'Lotte Bergtel-Schleif', class: 'ai-img' %>
          </div>
          <div class="ai-details">
            <h3>Lotte Bergtel-Schleif</h3>
            <div class="ai-meta">Anti-Nazi Resister | Knowledge Protector</div>
            <p>A German librarian and anti-Nazi resistance agent. In the early 1930s, she risked her life by aiding those persecuted by the Nazis and disseminating anti-Nazi literature. Even after being imprisoned by the Gestapo, her resolve never wavered. Her work as a librarian and a resister reminds us that protecting knowledge and fighting oppression often go hand in hand.</p>
          </div>
        </article>

        <article class="ai-card animate-card">
          <div class="ai-image">
            <%= image_tag 'Florence_Mendheim.png', alt: 'Florence Mendheim', class: 'ai-img' %>
          </div>
          <div class="ai-details">
            <h3>Florence Mendheim</h3>
            <div class="ai-meta">Undercover Defender | Democracy Guardian</div>
            <p>A Jewish librarian at the New York Public Library during the 1930s. As the Nazi movement gained traction in the United States, she infiltrated pro-Nazi organizations under the pseudonym "Gertrude Mueller," gathering intelligence and documenting their propaganda efforts. Her courage in confronting fascist ideologies on American soil highlights the vital role librarians play in defending freedom of information and democracy.</p>
          </div>
        </article>
      </div>
    </section>
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  /* Modern Color Scheme */
  :root {
    --primary: #2A5C82;
    --secondary: #F5A623;
    --accent: #3AB795;
    --dark: #1A2B3C;
    --light: #F8F9FA;
    --gradient-primary: linear-gradient(135deg, #2A5C82 0%, #3AB795 100%);
    --gradient-secondary: linear-gradient(135deg, #F5A623 0%, #FF6F61 100%);
  }

  /* Typography */
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@500;600;700&family=Open+Sans:wght@400;600&display=swap');

  body {
    font-family: 'Open Sans', sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--dark);
    overflow-x: hidden;
  }

  h1, h2, h3 {
    font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  /* Animations */
  @keyframes slideInLeft {
    from {
      transform: translateX(-100%);
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      transform: translateX(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  @keyframes slideInRight {
    from {
      transform: translateX(100%);
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      transform: translateX(0);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  @keyframes scaleUp {
    from {
      transform: scale(0.8);
      opacity: 0;
    }
    to {
      transform: scale(1);
      opacity: 1;
    }
  }

  @keyframes fadeIn {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(20px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes headerSlide {
    from {
      opacity: 0;
      transform: translateY(-50px);
    }
    to {
      opacity: 1;
      transform: translateY(0);
    }
  }

  @keyframes gradientShift {
    0% {
      background-position: 0% 50%;
    }
    50% {
      background-position: 100% 50%;
    }
    100% {
      background-position: 0% 50%;
    }
  }

  .animate-header {
    animation: headerSlide 1s ease-out;
  }

  .animate-accent {
    animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out 0.3s backwards;
  }

  .animate-slide-left {
    animation: slideInLeft 1s ease-out;
  }

  .animate-slide-right {
    animation: slideInRight 1s ease-out;
  }

  .animate-scale {
    animation: scaleUp 1s ease-out;
  }

  .animate-fade-in {
    animation: fadeIn 1s ease-out;
  }

  .animate-card {
    animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  /* Header Section */
  .about-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
    position: relative;
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    font-size: 3.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    position: relative;
    display: inline-block;
    background: var(--gradient-primary);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .header-accent {
    width: 60px;
    height: 4px;
    background: var(--gradient-secondary);
    margin: 0 auto;
    border-radius: 2px;
    animation: gradientShift 5s infinite;
  }

  /* Profile Sections */
  .profile-section {
    padding: 2rem 0;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(20px);
    animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease-out forwards;
  }

  .profile-content {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    gap: 2rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .profile-image .image-wrapper {
    width: 250px;
    height: 250px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 4px solid var(--primary);
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .profile-image:hover .image-wrapper {
    transform: scale(1.05);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
  }

  .profile-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
  }

  .profile-text {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .profile-text h2 {
    font-size: 2.2rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gradient-primary);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .highlight {
    color: var(--primary);
  }

  blockquote {
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    border-left: 4px solid var(--secondary);
    padding-left: 2rem;
    margin: 2rem 0;
    color: var(--dark);
    font-style: italic;
    background: var(--light);
    padding: 1.5rem;
    border-radius: 8px;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  /* Mission Section */
  .mission-section {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--light) 0%, #ffffff 100%);
    padding: 6rem 0;
    margin: 6rem 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .mission-content {
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    display: flex;
    gap: 4rem;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .mission-visual {
    position: relative;
    flex: 0 0 300px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    align-items: center;
  }

  .logo-container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 250px;
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
  }

  .mission-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    border-radius: 8px;
    object-fit: contain;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 10px 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1));
  }

  .visual-accent {
    position: absolute;
    width: calc(100% + 30px);
    height: calc(100% + 30px);
    background: var(--gradient-secondary);
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    border-radius: 12px;
    z-index: 1;
    transition: all 0.5s ease;
    animation: gradientShift 5s infinite;
  }

  .mission-visual:hover .visual-accent {
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%) rotate(2deg);
  }

  .mission-text h2 {
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    background: var(--gradient-primary);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .lead {
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  /* AI Section */
  .ai-section {
    margin: 6rem 0;
  }

  .ai-intro {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 4rem;
  }

  .ai-intro h2 {
    font-size: 2.4rem;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    background: var(--gradient-primary);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
  }

  .subheading {
    color: var(--primary);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .ai-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
    gap: 3rem;
    max-width: 1200px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .ai-card {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 10px;
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: 0 5px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease, box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-10px);
    box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
  }

  .ai-img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 200px;
    object-fit: cover;
    filter: grayscale(100%);
    transition: filter 0.3s ease;
  }

  .ai-card:hover .ai-img {
    filter: grayscale(0%);
  }

  .ai-details {
    padding: 2rem;
  }

  .ai-details h3 {
    color: var(--primary);
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
  }

  .ai-meta {
    color: var(--secondary);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .profile-content,
    .mission-content {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .mission-visual {
      max-width: 250px;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }

    .visual-accent {
      width: calc(100% + 20px);
      height: calc(100% + 20px);
    }

    .about-header h1 {
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }
  }
</style>